column1: NO2: annual mean concentrations and exceedance flag
above_LV? = 1 if round(statistic_value,0) > 40; round(statistic_value,0) means that statistic_value is rounded to an integer value
column7: count_type_by_city: count of station of the same type (traffic or background) within the same city. Note: one station_european_code can be counted several times if the same station shows several concentration statistics for the same year (distinct measurements recorded under different measurement_european_group_code)
in the case of a traffic station: assigned_population=(UA_city_pop*percentage_taffic_population/100)/count_type_by_city
in the case of a background station: assigned_population=(UA_city_pop*percentage_background_population/100)/count_type_by_city
